{
  "texts": [
    "The ANCOVA result showed that the UI conditions had a significant impact on token-based opinion length after controlling individual factors (F (3,839) = 2.80, p < 0.05).",
    "We observed that two individual factors (covariates), i.e., interest in themes (F (1,839) = 9.21, p < 0.01) and knowledge on themes (F (1,839) = 4.62, p < 0.05), significantly affected the opinion length.",
    "The post hoc tests revealed that the participants using the SUGGESTIVE bot wrote longer opinions compared to those using the PLAIN bot (mean: 109.9 tokens vs. 97.0 tokens; p(suggestiveplain) < 0.05).",
    "No significant difference was observed between the SUGGESTIVE ++ and PLAIN bots (p > 0.05), although the mean opinion length of the SUGGESTIVE ++ bot was higher than that of the SUGGESTIVE bot (mean: 114.5 vs. 109.9).",
    "Furthermore, no significant difference was observed between the EXPOSITVE and PLAIN bots."
  ]
}